name: MacBMD-X
tagline: OS X client for the FreeBMD genealogy database
body:
### Welcome to The MacBMD-X project page

Unless you are an active transcriber for the FreeBMD project you have no use for this software. So don't bother looking at it!

Please refer to the main FreeBMD project webpage at http://freebmd.rootsweb.com/ for more info
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
